channel.title: Need help with 508
channel.description:
Hi im trying to get a 508 when i start up my server because i really like them. Anywayz i got one and i understand the concept of them. The only thing i cant seem to get to work is making myself owner of the server... Now dont be stupid saying "oh you have to go into login.java and change your name from the other persons name" ive tried that like 10 thousand times on 10 thousand different 508 sources. NONE OF THEM WORKED. so anyway it would be nice if u could tell me how u really do it because obviously theres more to it that im missing. Please and thank you,
-coolpup2233-

item.title: Need help with 508

item.description:

Dude, you need to compile. First when you open server files, go and that named ‘‘CMD’’ then press on that named ‘‘Rs2>io’’ then restart server.
